title: U2 - Bullet the Blue Sky & Van Diemens Land(Singles) 320k m
description:
Description
U2 Rattle and Hum I think it was the last album where I found what i was looking for (pardon the pun) And there are a lot of great tracks on the album but for me these 2 stood out head and shoulders above the rest. I think it was the last time that they were taking shots at the corporate world. Before they became it. Anyway I threw these 2 out there cause they sounded so good that I had to have them somewhere in my pages. Thanks to vtwin88cube  CD rip of this. I still have the cassette but that don't help much anymore
